  <li class="comment-item" data-cid="3889960236">
    <div class="comment">
      <h3>
        <span class="comment-vote">
            <span id="c-3889960236" class="vote-count">0</span>
              <a id="btn-3889960236" href="" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="3889960236">有用</a>

        </span>
        <span class="comment-info">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/153306203/">龙城飞将</a>
            <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
          <a class="comment-time" href="/comment/3889960236">2023-09-06 22:30:14</a>
          <span class="comment-location">贵州</span>
        </span>
      </h3>
      <p class="comment-content">
      
        <span class="short">大概两年没看金庸先生作品了。石破天和石中玉的情节，回想金先生作品类似双胞胎酷似情节的还有《书剑恩仇录》里的陈家洛和福康安。当然，两者不一样。本书不算大篇幅，人物依然栩栩如生，丁不三不四两兄弟、白自在史婆婆夫妇、石清夫妇、丁当阿绣、张三李四都很性格突出。尤其是本书修改幅度很小，所以更好。末尾包括短篇《越女剑》和《三十三剑客图》，后者很有《聊斋》的感觉。</span>
      </p>
        <div class="report-comment" data-url="https://book.douban.com/subject/1212894/?comment_id=3889960236"></div>
    </div>
  </li>

          
